data.title: Trailer Hitch Install: CURT 13360 on Ford F-150
data.tags: CURT Receiver Hitch, trailer hitch, towing, how to install, Ford F150, F-150, curt 13360
data.description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 13360 Class 3 trailer hitch on a 2008 Ford F-150.

Install Sheet: 
https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/13360/installsheet/CM_13360_INS.PDF

No drilling required.

Application Coverage:
2006 - 2008 Ford F-150 Except without factory Hitch
2006 - 2008 Lincoln LT

PERIODICALLY CHECK THIS RECEIVER HITCH TO ENSURE THAT ALL FASTENERS
ARE TIGHT AND THAT ALL STRUCTURAL COMPONENTS ARE SOUND.
*** USE EXISTING VEHICLE HARDWARE ***
